      "updated": 1382799600,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "6090ec30aff09e00003dea42",
      "text": " 前回は西田幾多郎の「<a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/4000015656/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=247&creative=7399&creativeASIN=4000015656&linkCode=as2&tag=nishiohirokaz-22\">哲学概論</a>」を読んだ。次は中島義道の「<a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/4061594818/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=247&creative=7399&creativeASIN=4061594818&linkCode=as2&tag=nishiohirokaz-22\">哲学の教科書</a>」を読むつもり。",
      "created": 1382799600,
      "updated": 1382799600,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
